content.title: On Earth
content.content:
1907 - Author Paul H. Kocher is born.
1925 - Sir Gawain and the Green Knight is first published.
1944 - J.R.R. Tolkien writes Letter 62.
1957 - Poet Roy Campbell dies.
1986 - Voice actor Otto Preminger dies.
1987 - Pictures under Discussion is published.
2010 - Musician and composer Bo Hansson dies.
2020 - Actor Bruce Allpress dies.
